high_descs: Go forward to the counter and turn right to go to the sink.
Pick up the knife laying vertically on the side of the sink.
Turn right, step forward and then turn left to be center with the sink.
Slice the potato in the center of the sink.
Turn left, step forward and look up on the shelf.
Put the knife upright in the tomato next to the kettle.
Return to the kitchen sink.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn around, step forward then turn right to go to the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the potato slice inside close the door and turn on.  Wait till microwave is off and remove the potato.
Turn right and go to the edge of the counter, then turn left to face the tomato.
Lean the potato against the green apple to the right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a slice of potato and put it against the apple.

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room to face the sink.
Pick up the knife on the sink.
Take a step to the right to face the right side of the sink.
cut the potato in the sink into slices.
Turn left and step forward to face the tomato on the back of the counter.
Place the knife on the tomato on the back of the counter.
Turn right to face the potato in the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato in the sink.
Turn left and step forward to face the microwave.
Heat the potato slice in the microwave and remove it.
Take a step to the right to face the back of the counter.
Place the potato slice to the right of the tomato on the back of the counter.
anns.task_desc: To heat a potato slice and place it on the back of the counter to the right of the tomato.

high_descs: Go forward, turn right and go to the sink
Pick up the knife to the left of the sink
Move a bit to the right
Slice the potato in the sink
Turn left, go forward to the counter
Put the knife on the counter
Turn around, go forward, turn left at the sink
Pick up a potato slice from the sink
Turn around, go forward, turn right and go to the microwave
Put the potato slice in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the potato slice from the microwave
Turn right, go forward, turn left
Put the potato slice on the counter
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, cook a slice of potato in the microwave
